Package com.paypal.selion.platform.dataprovider

A collection of classes to support connecting to data sources and performing operations on the GUI Map data.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractExcelDataProvider
    This class provide several methods to retrieve test data from an Excel workbook.
    DefaultCustomType
    This class represents a custom type that should automatically be handled.
    FileSystemResource
    FileSystemResource defines the file path and file name of the data source to be used for data provider consumption.
    SimpleExcelDataProvider
    This class provide several methods to retrieve test data from an Excel workbook.
    YamlDataProvider
    This class provides several methods to retrieve test data from yaml files.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DataProviderException
    This Exception class is specific to data reader.
    ExcelDataProviderException
    This Exception is supposed to wrap exceptions thrown While trying to read an Excel file
    YamlDataProviderException
    This exception is supposed to wrap exception being thrown while reading a YAML file.
